\ninformation), but not limited to: <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-top:1.5pt;margin-right:7.5pt;\r\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:36.75pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-add-space:auto;\r\nline-height:normal;tab-stops:45.8pt 91.6pt 137.4pt 183.2pt 229.0pt 274.8pt 320.6pt 366.4pt 412.2pt 458.0pt 503.8pt 549.6pt 595.4pt 641.2pt 687.0pt 732.8pt;\r\nbackground:#FEFEFE\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, &quot;serif&quot;; letter-spacing: 0.25pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Email<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-top:1.5pt;margin-right:7.5pt;\r\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:36.75pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-add-space:auto;\r\nline-height:normal;tab-stops:45.8pt 91.6pt 137.4pt 183.2pt 229.0pt 274.8pt 320.6pt 366.4pt 412.2pt 458.0pt 503.8pt 549.6pt 595.4pt 641.2pt 687.0pt 732.8pt;\r\nbackground:#FEFEFE\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, &quot;serif&quot;; letter-spacing: 0.25pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Full name <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-top:1.5pt;margin-right:7.5pt;\r\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:36.75pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-add-space:auto;\r\nline-height:normal;tab-stops:45.8pt 91.6pt 137.4pt 183.2pt 229.0pt 274.8pt 320.6pt 366.4pt 412.2pt 458.0pt 503.8pt 549.6pt 595.4pt 641.2pt 687.0pt 732.8pt;\r\nbackground:#FEFEFE\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, &quot;serif&quot;; letter-spacing: 0.25pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Address <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-top:1.5pt;margin-right:7.5pt;\r\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:36.75pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-add-space:auto;\r\nline-height:normal;tab-stops:45.8pt 91.6pt 137.4pt 183.2pt 229.0pt 274.8pt 320.6pt 366.4pt 412.2pt 458.0pt 503.8pt 549.6pt 595.4pt 641.2pt 687.0pt 732.8pt;\r\nbackground:#FEFEFE\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, &quot;serif&quot;; letter-spacing: 0.25pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Mobile<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:1.5pt;margin-right:7.5pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0in;margin-left:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:normal;tab-stops:45.8pt 91.6pt 137.4pt 183.2pt 229.0pt 274.8pt 320.6pt 366.4pt 412.2pt 458.0pt 503.8pt 549.6pt 595.4pt 641.2pt 687.0pt 732.8pt;\r\nbackground:#FEFEFE\"><b><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#17365D;mso-themecolor:text2;\r\nmso-themeshade:191;letter-spacing:.25pt;mso-bidi-language:BN-BD\">2 Usage Data :</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, &quot;serif&quot;; letter-spacing: 0.25pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:1.5pt;margin-right:7.5pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0in;margin-left:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:normal;tab-stops:45.8pt 91.6pt 137.4pt 183.2pt 229.0pt 274.8pt 320.6pt 366.4pt 412.2pt 458.0pt 503.8pt 549.6pt 595.4pt 641.2pt 687.0pt 732.8pt;\r\nbackground:#FEFEFE\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, &quot;serif&quot;; letter-spacing: 0.25pt;\">We may also collect information about how the Service\r\nis accessed and used (Usage Data). This Usage Data may include information such\r\nas your computer’s Internet Protocol address (e.g. IP address), browser type,\r\nbrowser version, the pages of our Service that you visit, the time and date of\r\nyour visit, the time spent on those pages, unique device identifiers and other\r\ndiagnostic data.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:1.5pt;margin-right:7.5pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0in;margin-left:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:normal;tab-stops:45.8pt 91.6pt 137.4pt 183.2pt 229.0pt 274.8pt 320.6pt 366.4pt 412.2pt 458.0pt 503.8pt 549.6pt 595.4pt 641.2pt 687.0pt 732.8pt;\r\nbackground:#FEFEFE\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, &quot;serif&quot;; letter-spacing: 0.25pt;\">The website &amp;amp; app does use third party\r\nservices that may collect information used to identify you.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:1.5pt;margin-right:7.5pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0in;margin-left:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:normal;tab-stops:45.8pt 91.6pt 137.4pt 183.2pt 229.0pt 274.8pt 320.6pt 366.4pt 412.2pt 458.0pt 503.8pt 549.6pt 595.4pt 641.2pt 687.0pt 732.8pt;\r\nbackground:#FEFEFE\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, &quot;serif&quot;; letter-spacing: 0.25pt;\">Link to privacy policy of third party service providers\r\nused by the website &amp; app Google Play Services.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:1.5pt;margin-right:7.5pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0in;margin-left:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:normal;tab-stops:45.8pt 91.6pt 137.4pt 183.2pt 229.0pt 274.8pt 320.6pt 366.4pt 412.2pt 458.0pt 503.8pt 549.6pt 595.4pt 641.2pt 687.0pt 732.8pt;\r\nbackground:#FEFEFE\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, &quot;serif&quot;; letter-spacing: 0.25pt;\">AdMob<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:1.5pt;margin-right:7.5pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0in;margin-left:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:normal;tab-stops:45.8pt 91.6pt 137.4pt 183.2pt 229.0pt 274.8pt 320.6pt 366.4pt 412.2pt 458.0pt 503.8pt 549.6pt 595.4pt 641.2pt 687.0pt 732.8pt;\r\nbackground:#FEFEFE\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, &quot;serif&quot;; letter-spacing: 0.25pt;\">Google Analytics for Firebase<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:1.5pt;margin-right:7.5pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0in;margin-left:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:normal;tab-stops:45.8pt 91.6pt 137.4pt 183.2pt 229.0pt 274.8pt 320.6pt 366.4pt 412.2pt 458.0pt 503.8pt 549.6pt 595.4pt 641.2pt 687.0pt 732.8pt;\r\nbackground:#FEFEFE\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, &quot;serif&quot;; letter-spacing: 0.25pt;\">Firebase Crashlytics<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:1.5pt;margin-right:7.5pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0in;margin-left:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:normal;tab-stops:45.8pt 91.6pt 137.4pt 183.2pt 229.0pt 274.8pt 320.6pt 366.4pt 412.2pt 458.0pt 503.8pt 549.6pt 595.4pt 641.2pt 687.0pt 732.8pt;\r\nbackground:#FEFEFE\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, &quot;serif&quot;; letter-spacing: 0.25pt;\">Facebook</span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;; letter-spacing: 0.25pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:1.5pt;margin-right:7.5pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0in;margin-left:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:normal;tab-stops:45.8pt 91.6pt 137.4pt 183.2pt 229.0pt 274.8pt 320.6pt 366.4pt 412.2pt 458.0pt 503.8pt 549.6pt 595.4pt 641.2pt 687.0pt 732.8pt;\r\nbackground:#FEFEFE\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, &quot;serif&quot;; letter-spacing: 0.25pt;\">One Signal<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, &quot;serif&quot;; color: rgb(23, 54, 93); letter-spacing: 0.25pt;\">2.1 Login Data :</span></span><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:1.5pt;margin-right:7.5pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0in;margin-left:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:normal;tab-stops:45.8pt 91.6pt 137.4pt 183.2pt 229.0pt 274.8pt 320.6pt 366.4pt 412.2pt 458.0pt 503.8pt 549.6pt 595.4pt 641.2pt 687.0pt 732.8pt;\r\nbackground:#FEFEFE\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:#1B1B28\">We want to inform you that whenever you use our Service, in a\r\ncase of an error in the app we collect data and information (through third\r\nparty products) on your phone called Log Data. This Log Data may include\r\ninformation such as your device Internet Protocol (“IP”) address, device name,\r\noperating system version, the configuration of the app when utilizing our\r\nService, the time and date of your use of the Service, and other statistics.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:1.5pt;margin-right:7.5pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0in;margin-left:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:normal;tab-stops:45.8pt 91.6pt 137.4pt 183.2pt 229.0pt 274.8pt 320.6pt 366.4pt 412.2pt 458.0pt 503.8pt 549.6pt 595.4pt 641.2pt 687.0pt 732.8pt;\r\nbackground:#FEFEFE\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, &quot;serif&quot;; color: rgb(23, 54, 93); letter-spacing: 0.25pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">3 Tracking and cookies data</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, &quot;serif&quot;; letter-spacing: 0.25pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"> <o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:1.5pt;margin-right:7.5pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0in;margin-left:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:normal;tab-stops:45.8pt 91.6pt 137.4pt 183.2pt 229.0pt 274.8pt 320.6pt 366.4pt 412.2pt 458.0pt 503.8pt 549.6pt 595.4pt 641.2pt 687.0pt 732.8pt;\r\nbackground:#FEFEFE\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, &quot;serif&quot;; letter-spacing: 0.25pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">We use cookies and similar\r\ntracking technology to track the activity of our services and we keep certain\r\ninformation. Cookies are files containing a small amount of data that may\r\ncontain an anonymous unique identifier. Cookies are sent from a website to your\r\nbrowser and stored on your device. Other tracking technologies such as beacons,\r\ntags and scripts are also used to collect and track information and to improve\r\nand analyze our services. You can tell your browser to reject all cookies or to\r\nindicate when a cookie is being sent. However, if you do not accept cookies,\r\nyou will not be able to use any part of our services.<o:p></o:p></span></p><pre style=\"margin-top:1.5pt;margin-right:7.5pt;margin-bottom:3.75pt;\r\nmargin-left:0in;tab-stops:45.8pt 91.6pt 137.4pt;background:#FEFEFE\"><b><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#17365D;\r\nmso-themecolor:text2;mso-themeshade:191;letter-spacing:.25pt\">4 Data Collection Research</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:black;\r\nletter-spacing:.25pt\">&nbsp; <o:p></o:p></span></b></pre><pre style=\"margin-top:1.5pt;margin-right:7.5pt;margin-bottom:3.75pt;margin-left:\r\n0in;background:#FEFEFE\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:black;letter-spacing:.25pt\">We always strive to research our customers\' information.<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre style=\"margin-top:1.5pt;margin-right:7.5pt;margin-bottom:3.75pt;margin-left:\r\n0in;background:#FEFEFE\"><b><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:#17365D;mso-themecolor:text2;mso-themeshade:191;letter-spacing:.25pt\">5 Disclosure of personal information</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:black;\r\nletter-spacing:.25pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></pre><pre style=\"margin-top:1.5pt;\r\nmargin-right:7.5pt;margin-bottom:3.75pt;margin-left:0in;background:#FEFEFE\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:black;\r\nletter-spacing:.25pt\">5.1 Business transactions :<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre style=\"margin-top:1.5pt;margin-right:7.5pt;margin-bottom:3.75pt;margin-left:\r\n0in;background:#FEFEFE\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:black;letter-spacing:.25pt\">If the company is involved in mergers, acquisitions or sale of assets,Then your personal data may be transferred. We will publish notifications before your personal data is transferred and subject to a different privacy policy.<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre style=\"margin-top:1.5pt;margin-right:7.5pt;margin-bottom:3.75pt;margin-left:\r\n0in;background:#FEFEFE\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nletter-spacing:.25pt\">5.2 Law enforcement :<span style=\"color:black\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></pre><pre style=\"margin-top:1.5pt;margin-right:7.5pt;margin-bottom:3.75pt;margin-left:\r\n7.5pt;background:#FEFEFE\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:black;letter-spacing:.25pt\">The Company may disclose your personal data if it is required to do so in response to a legitimate request by law or by a government authority (such as a court or government agency).<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre style=\"margin-top:1.5pt;margin-right:7.5pt;margin-bottom:3.75pt;margin-left:\r\n0in;background:#FEFEFE\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, &quot;serif&quot;; color: black; letter-spacing: 0.25pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">5.3 The security of your personal data is important to us, but keep in mind that transmissions via the Internet or electronic storage systems are not 100% secure. While we strive to use commercially acceptable means to protect your personal data, we cannot guarantee its absolute security.<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre style=\"margin-top:1.5pt;margin-right:7.5pt;margin-bottom:3.75pt;margin-left:\r\n0in;background:#FEFEFE\"><b><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:#244061;mso-themecolor:accent1;mso-themeshade:128;letter-spacing:.25pt\">6 Children\'s privacy</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:black;\r\nletter-spacing:.25pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></pre><pre style=\"margin-top:1.5pt;\r\nmargin-right:7.5pt;margin-bottom:3.75pt;margin-left:0in;background:#FEFEFE\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:black;\r\nletter-spacing:.25pt\">Our service does not address anyone under the age of 13 (\"child\").<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre style=\"margin-top:1.5pt;margin-right:7.5pt;margin-bottom:3.75pt;margin-left:\r\n0in;background:#FEFEFE\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:black;letter-spacing:.25pt\">We do not knowingly collect personally identifiable information from anyone under the age of 13. If you are a parent and you know your child is providing our personal data, please contact us. If we become aware that we are collecting personal data from children without parental consent verification, we do not take immediate steps to remove the information from our servers.<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre style=\"margin-top:1.5pt;margin-right:7.5pt;margin-bottom:3.75pt;margin-left:\r\n0in;background:#FEFEFE\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:black;letter-spacing:.25pt\">This is a privacy policy change<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre style=\"margin-top:1.5pt;margin-right:7.5pt;margin-bottom:3.75pt;margin-left:\r\n0in;background:#FEFEFE\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:black;letter-spacing:.25pt\">We may update our privacy policy from time to time. We will notify you if we make any changes to this page by posting a new privacy policy.<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre style=\"margin-top:1.5pt;margin-right:7.5pt;margin-bottom:3.75pt;margin-left:\r\n0in;background:#FEFEFE\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:black;letter-spacing:.25pt\">We will notify you via email or a special notification on our service before the change takes effect and update the \"Acting Date\" at the top of this Privacy Policy.<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre style=\"margin-top:1.5pt;margin-right:7.5pt;margin-bottom:3.75pt;margin-left:\r\n0in;background:#FEFEFE\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:black;letter-spacing:.25pt\">You are advised to periodically review this Privacy Policy for any changes. Changes to this Privacy Policy take effect when they are posted on this page<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre style=\"margin-top:1.5pt;margin-right:7.5pt;margin-bottom:3.75pt;margin-left:\r\n0in;background:#FEFEFE\"><b><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:#244061;mso-themecolor:accent1;mso-themeshade:128;letter-spacing:.25pt\">7 Contact</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:black;\r\nletter-spacing:.25pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></pre><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:1.5pt;margin-right:7.5pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0in;margin-left:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:normal;tab-stops:45.8pt 91.6pt 137.4pt 183.2pt 229.0pt 274.8pt 320.6pt 366.4pt 412.2pt 458.0pt 503.8pt 549.6pt 595.4pt 641.2pt 687.0pt 732.8pt;\r\nbackground:#FEFEFE\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 15pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, &quot;serif&quot;; letter-spacing: 0.25pt;\">If\r\nyou have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us.</span><br></p>', 'en', '2022-01-03 16:10:14', '2022-01-03 19:29:14');
INSERT INTO `page_translations` (`id`, `page_id`, `title`, `content`, `lang`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(3, 5, 'Term Conditions Page', '<p style=\"margin-top:0in\"><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;color:#244061;\r\nmso-themecolor:accent1;mso-themeshade:128\">1. Terms of Use<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p style=\"margin-top:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">1.1 Welcome to Alif.com.bd.&nbsp;provides\r\naccess to the Alif.com.bd website or the mobile application/app or any other\r\nmedia (“Website”) to you subject to the terms and conditions (“Terms”) set out\r\non this page. By using the Website, you, a registered or guest user in terms of\r\nthe eligibility criteria set out herein (“User”) agree to be bound by the\r\nTerms. Please read them carefully as your continued usage of the Website, you\r\nsignify your agreement to be bound by these Terms. If you do not want to be\r\nbound by the Terms, you must not subscribe to or use the Website or our\r\nservices.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">1.2 By impliedly or\r\nexpressly accepting these Terms, you also accept and agree to be bound by Alif.com.bd\r\nPolicies (including but not limited to Privacy Policy available at https://Alif.com.bd/privacypolicy\r\nas amended from time to time.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">1.3 In these Terms,\r\nreferences to “you”, “User” shall mean the end user/customer accessing the\r\nWebsite, its contents and using the Services offered through the Website.\r\nReferences to the “Website”, “</span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;\">Alif online shop</span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">”, “Alif\r\nonline shop”, “Alif.com.bd”, “Alif.com.bd”, “we”, “us” and “our” shall mean the\r\nWebsite and/or </span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;\">Alif\r\nonline shop</span><span lang=\"BN-BD\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">.</span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">1.4 This Website may\r\nalso contain links to other websites, which are not operated by Alif.com.bd,\r\nand Alif.com.bd has no control over the linked sites and accepts no\r\nresponsibility for them or for any loss or damage that may arise from your use\r\nof them. Your use of the linked sites will be subject to the terms of use and\r\nservice contained within each such site.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">1.5 We reserve the\r\nright to change these Terms at any time. Such changes will be effective when\r\nposted on the Website. By continuing to use the Website after we post any such\r\nchanges, you accept the Terms as modified.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">1.6 These Terms will\r\ncontinue to apply until terminated by either You or Alif.com.bd in accordance\r\nwith the terms set out below:<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">1.7 The agreement with\r\nAlif.com.bd can be terminated by (i) not accessing the Website; or (ii) closing\r\nYour Account, if such option has been made available to You.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">1.8\r\nNotwithstanding the foregoing, these provisions set out in these Terms which by\r\ntheir very nature survive are meant to survive termination, shall survive the\r\ntermination/expiry of this agreement.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0in\"><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;color:#244061;\r\nmso-themecolor:accent1;mso-themeshade:128\">2. Eligibility</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p style=\"margin-top:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">2.1 Use of the Website\r\nis available only to such persons who can legally contract under the Contract\r\nAct, 1872.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">2.2 If you are a minor\r\ni.e. under the age of 18 years, you shall not register as a user of Alif.com.bd\r\nand shall not transact on or use the Website. As a minor if you wish to use or\r\ntransact on website, such use or transaction may be made by your legal guardian\r\nor parents on the Website. Alif.com.bd reserves the right to terminate your\r\nmembership and / or refuse to provide you with access to the website if it is\r\nbrought to Alif’s notice or if it is discovered that you are under the age of\r\n18 years.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">2.3 By accepting the\r\nTerms or using or transacting on the Website, the User irrevocably declares and\r\nundertakes that he/she is of legal age i.e. 18 years or older and capable of\r\nentering into a binding contract and such usage shall be deemed to form a\r\ncontract between the Website and such User to the extent permissible under\r\napplicable laws.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">2.4 The usage of the\r\nServices offered through the Website is only available if the address of the User\r\nto which the product(s) is/are to be delivered is within Gazipur,Bangladesh.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0in\"><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;color:#244061;\r\nmso-themecolor:accent1;mso-themeshade:128\">3. Communication</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p style=\"margin-top:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">3.1 When you use Alif.com.bd,\r\nor contact us via phone or email, you consent to receive communication from us.\r\nYou authorize us to communicate with you by e-mail, SMS, phone call by any\r\nother mode of communication. For contractual purposes, you consent to receive\r\ncommunications (including transactional, promotional and/or commercial\r\nmessages), from us with respect to your use of the website and/or your order\r\nplaced on the Website. Additionally any disclosures posted on the site, or sent\r\nto you by email fulfill the legal obligation of communication made in writing.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0in\"><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;color:#244061;\r\nmso-themecolor:accent1;mso-themeshade:128\">4. Your Account and Responsibilities</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p style=\"margin-top:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">4.1 Any person may\r\naccess the Website either by registering to the Website or using the Website as\r\na guest. However, a guest user may not have access to all sections of the\r\nWebsite including certain benefits/promotional offers, which shall be reserved\r\nonly for the purpose of registered Users, and which may change from time to\r\ntime at the sole discretion of the Website.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">4.2 If you wish to\r\nregister your account with the Website, you shall be required to create an\r\naccount by registering with a valid Bangladeshi mobile number and/or your email\r\naddress or by filling in the details prescribed in the Website registration\r\nform.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">4.3 If you use the\r\nwebsite, you will be responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your\r\nusername and password and you will be responsible for all activities that occur\r\nunder your username and you will be under the obligation to restrict access to\r\nyour computer or mobile phone to prevent unauthorized access to your account.\r\nYou should inform us immediately if you have any reason to believe that your\r\npassword has become known to anyone else, or if the password is being, or is\r\nlikely to be, used in an unauthorized manner. You agree that if you provide any\r\ninformation that is untrue, inaccurate, not current or incomplete or we have\r\nreasonable grounds to suspect that such information is untrue, inaccurate, not\r\ncurrent or incomplete, or not in accordance with this Terms of Use, we have the\r\nright to suspend or terminate your membership on the website.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">4.4 The Website may be\r\ninaccessible for such purposes as it may, at its sole discretion deem necessary,\r\nincluding but not limited to regular maintenance. However, under no\r\ncircumstances will Alif.com.bd be held liable for any losses or claims arising\r\nout of such inaccessibility to the Users and the Users expressly waive any\r\nclaims against Alif.com.bd in this regard<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0in\"><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;color:#244061;\r\nmso-themecolor:accent1;mso-themeshade:128\">5. Copyright</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p style=\"margin-top:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">5.1 The material\r\n(including the content, and any other content, software or services) contained\r\non alif.com.bd are the property of </span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;\">Alif</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n16.0pt\">, its subsidiaries, affiliates and/or third party licensors. No\r\nmaterial on this site may be copied, reproduced, republished, installed,\r\nposted, transmitted, stored or distributed without written permission from Alif.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">5.2 You may not use\r\nany “deep-link”, “page-scrape”, “robot”, “spider” or other automatic device,\r\nprogram, algorithm or methodology, or any similar or equivalent manual process,\r\nto access, acquire, copy or monitor any portion of the website or any content,\r\nor in any way reproduce or circumvent the navigational structure or\r\npresentation of the website or any content, to obtain or attempt to obtain any\r\nmaterials, documents or information through any means not purposely made\r\navailable through the website. We reserve our right to bar any such activity.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0in\"><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;color:#244061;\r\nmso-themecolor:accent1;mso-themeshade:128\">6. Cookies</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p style=\"margin-top:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">6.1 This site uses\r\ncookies, which means that you must have cookies enabled on your computer in\r\norder for all functionality on this site to work properly. A cookie is a small\r\ndata file that is written to your hard drive when you visit certain Websites.\r\nCookie files contain certain information, such as a random number user ID that\r\nthe site assigns to a visitor to track the pages visited. A cookie cannot read\r\ndata off your hard disk or read cookie files created by other sites. Cookies,\r\nby themselves, cannot be used to find out the identity of any user.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0in\"><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;color:#244061;\r\nmso-themecolor:accent1;mso-themeshade:128\">7. Promotional Activity</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p style=\"margin-top:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">7.1 To promote its\r\nservices elabiba.com.bd uses various advertisements and commercials which are\r\ntruthful and are not deceptive or unfair to the best of our knowledge and\r\nbelief. Every user is under the obligation to go through the relevant\r\ninformation contained in the Website before using the service and it will be\r\nassumed that each user is aware of every information provided in the Website.\r\nImages of products in the Website are for and by reference only and actual\r\nproducts may vary from the corresponding image exhibited. The Website disclaims\r\nany liabilities arising out of any discrepancies to this end to the fullest\r\nextent permitted by law.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0in\"><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;color:#244061;\r\nmso-themecolor:accent1;mso-themeshade:128\">8. The Contract</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p style=\"margin-top:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">8.1 Your order is an\r\noffer to us to buy the product(s) in your order. When you place an order to\r\npurchase a product from us, you will receive an e-mail confirming receipt of\r\nyour order and/or containing the details of your order (the “Order Confirmation\r\nE-mail and/or SMS”). The Order Confirmation E-mail and/or SMS is\r\nacknowledgement that we have received your order, but does not confirm\r\nacceptance of your offer to buy the product(s) ordered; that when we send the\r\nOrder Confirmation E-mail and/or SMS a contract called an “agreement to sell”\r\nis concluded in accordance with Section 4(3) of the Sale of Goods Act, 1930\r\ni.e. the transfer of the property in the goods is to take place at a future\r\ntime when the product(s) is/are delivered to your designated address. We only\r\naccept your offer, and the above “agreement to sell” becomes a contract of sale\r\nfor product(s) ordered by you in accordance with Section 4(4) of the Sale of\r\nGoods Act, 1930, when the product(s) is/are delivered to your designated\r\naddress and at that time the property in the goods is transferred from us to\r\nyou.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">8.2 Please note that\r\nwe sell products only in quantities which correspond to the typical needs of an\r\naverage household. This applies both to the number of products ordered within a\r\nsingle order and the placing of several orders for the same product where the\r\nindividual orders comprise a quantity typical for a normal household.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0in\"><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;color:#244061;\r\nmso-themecolor:accent1;mso-themeshade:128\">9. Product Descriptions</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p style=\"margin-top:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">10.1 Alif.com.bd\r\nattempts to be as accurate as possible. Alif.com.bd does not manufacture or\r\nproduce any product by themselves. Therefore, elabiba.com.bd does not warrant\r\nthat product descriptions or other content of any Alif.com.bd product is\r\naccurate, complete, reliable, current, or error-free. If a product offered by Alif.com.bd\r\nitself is not as described, your sole remedy is to return it in unused\r\ncondition.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0in\"><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;color:#244061;\r\nmso-themecolor:accent1;mso-themeshade:128\">10. Pricing</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p style=\"margin-top:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">11.1 Except where\r\nnoted otherwise, the list price or suggested price displayed for products on Alif.com.bd\r\nrepresents the full retail price listed on the product itself, suggested by the\r\nmanufacturer or supplier, or estimated in accordance with standard industry\r\npractice; or the estimated retail value for a comparably featured item offered\r\nelsewhere. The list price or suggested price is a comparative price estimate\r\nand may or may not represent the prevailing price in every area on any\r\nparticular day.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0in\"><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;color:#244061;\r\nmso-themecolor:accent1;mso-themeshade:128\">11. Refund Policy</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p style=\"margin-top:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">11.1 Alif.com.bd tries\r\nits best to serve the users. But if under any